author: Inside Edition
description: High school football coach Travis Turner was revered in the small town of Big Stone Gap, Virginia. Turner was named coach of the year in 2021 by a local newspaper. His father also coached high school football. Turner's glowing reputation imploded after authorities announced he is now wanted for allegedly possessing child pornography. Turner's wife, Leslie, spoke out about the allegations against her husband saying, "None of that is true. He's a good dad and a good husband, and we want him home."
title: He Was Revered In Small Town, Now He's Wanted For Child Pornography

author: Inside Edition
description: President Donald Trump is fired up Wednesday after The New York Times claims he is showing "signs of fatigue." They reported that Trump's official appearances have decreased by 39%. Trump hit back at the report on social media and got personal. The Times is standing by writer Katie Rogers, who they call an "expert" and "thorough" reporter.
title: Trump Fires Back After Report Says He's Showing 'Signs Of Fatigue'

author: Inside Edition
description: Two guests at a four-star restaurant asked to see inside the eatery's wine cellar and the co-owner obliged. The owner says while the woman distracted him with questions, her accomplice allegedly slipped six bottles of wine worth $38,000 under his coat. A chase was on. Another customer, Ryan Dotson leapt into his $200,000 Porsche and took off after the suspects with senior waiter Drew Chaney and caught the woman. Inside Edition spoke with co-owner of L'Auberge Provencale, Christian Borel.
title: Restaurant Guests Run Away With $38,000 Worth of Wine: Cops

author: Inside Edition
description: Four members of one family left Clearwater, Florida, on board a 25-foot catamaran to celebrate Dennis Woods’ 70th birthday and brought along his 90-year-old uncle, Clarence. Disaster struck when the boat flipped upside down. The family was stranded for 21 hours around 25 miles away from shore. Inside Edition spoke with Clarence. GoFundMe has been set up to rescue the boat. For further information about their GoFundMe, click this link: https://bit.ly/4pCnbQj
title: Family Stranded For 21 Hours After Boat Capsizes

author: Inside Edition
description: The "air walk" is America's latest dance craze blowing up on social media. Ballerinas, little kids, and couples are taking part in it. The air walk is inspired by "Dancing With The Stars" finalist Dylan Efron, Zac Efron's younger brother. He nailed the move with his partner, Daniella. On Tuesday night Robert Irwin was declared king of the ballroom. The wildlife expert's older sister, Bindi, who won the mirror ball trophy in 2015, ran in for a celebratory hug.
title: 'Air Walk' Goes Viral, Robert Irwin Wins 'Dancing With The Stars'

author: Inside Edition
description: Transportation Secretary Sean Duffy released an announcement telling people to dress better when they fly. His request is being met with mixed reviews. Duffy's request harkens back to a time when women looked elegant in pearls and dresses and men were decked out in suits while flying. It was also a time when airplanes were spacious with five more inches of leg room. Inside Edition went to Newark Airport in New Jersey and LAX in Los Angeles to speak with passengers responding to Duffy's call.
title: Dress Better When You Fly, Transportation Secretary Says

author: Inside Edition
description:
Chef Lauren Covas gave Inside Edition some tips to help elevate your Thanksgiving dinner. She took a plain can of green beans and cream of mushroom soup and made a green bean casserole. She topped it with canned crispy onions. She bumped up Stove Top stuffing several notches with carrots, celery, onion, garlic, and browned sausage. Even lettuce can be elevated. Ayesha Nurdjaja of Shukette Restaurant showed Inside Edition how to make a fall salad.

author: Inside Edition
description: Legendary NASCAR champion Kyle Busch and his wife Samantha say they lost $8.5 million on a complex insurance policy from Pacific Life. Now they're suing, alleging they were lied to by their life insurance agent and the policy contained hidden fees and was designed to rake in huge commissions. Pacific Life says that they’ve been in touch with the Busch’s and take their concerns seriously. They also say they stand behind all their policies and have helped millions plan for future financial security.
title: Legendary NASCAR Champion Says He Was Scammed Out Of Millions

author: Inside Edition
description: It's a love story for the ages. Leatrice and Stanley Dvoskin's relationship started back in 1949 with a little white lie about a lost earring. The couple, who now live in a senior apartment building in New Jersey, just celebrated 75 years of marriage. Their home displays the special moments of their lives, prominently featuring their three daughters, five grandkids and eight great grandkids. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Couple Married 75 Years Enjoys Nightly Happy Hour And Lots Of Laughs

author: Inside Edition
description: Authorities say Virginia high school football coach Travis Turner, who has gone missing, is wanted for allegedly possessing child sexual abuse materials. Police say Turner disappeared when they were on their way to his home as part of an investigation.
title: Cops Say Missing Football Coach Is Fugitive #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: Melinda Howard says she was breaking down cardboard boxes for recycling at her new house in Mississippi when she nicked her hand.
title: Woman's Paper Cut Led To Medical Emergency #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: One cheerleader was in for a big surprise in front of 60,000 fans. Mark Geist, also a Tennessee Titans cheerleader, needed to ask Kinley Propes something at a game against the Seattle Seahawks. With her beloved on one knee, stunned Propes couldn't believe it. She said yes and the halftime crowd went wild. Sliding the ring onto Propes' finger, the couple sealed things with a kiss. Inside Edition spoke with the bride and groom to be.
title: This Cheerleader Is In For Big Surprise In Front of 60,000 Fans
